                    "-DskipTests",
                    "-Dquarkus.package.type=legacy-jar"), Collections.emptyMap());

    await().atMost(1, TimeUnit.MINUTES).until(() -> result.getProcess() != null && !result.getProcess().isAlive());
    assertThat(running.log()).containsIgnoringCase("BUILD SUCCESS");
